Class BooleanMonitorImpl

    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BooleanMonitor, ItemFeatureEntry

    public class BooleanMonitorImpl
extends ItemFeatureEntryImpl
implements BooleanMonitor
    An implementation of the model object 'Boolean Monitor'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Reference Value
    • Active
    • Demote Prefix
    • Severity
    • Message
    • Suppress Events
    • Require Ack
